[normal]).
[normal] 
[normal]It is noteworthy that, like press coverage, the greatest emphasis came at a time when the Prime Minister, Chancellor and 
[normal]DECC 
[normal]Minister all strove 
[normal]persistently 
[normal]to 
[normal]make 
[normal]climate 
[normal]change 
[normal]a high profile issue at the heart of government (
[normal]with 
[normal]Opposition leader
[normal]s
[normal] compelled to position 
[normal]themselves 
[normal]accordingly). The current situation has seen both a drop in press and television coverage, 
[normal]at a time when 
[normal]climate change 
[normal]is 
[normal]given a much lower profile by 
[normal]significant figures in 
[normal]the government.
