[normal]its absence
[normal]) is an issue here. 
[normal]Finally, 
[normal]the vast bulk of documentaries were on 
[normal]niche
[normal] channels
[normal] 
[normal]characterised by low audience
[normal]s
[normal] 
[normal](BBC2, BBC3, BBC4, and
[normal] to a much lesser extent, on
